Templates.constructorDescription:
Constructor for a new LandscapeViewer. Accepts an object literal mSettings that defines initial property values, aggregated and associated objects as well as event handlers. See {@link sap.ui.base.ManagedObject#constructor} for a general description of the syntax of the settings object.

The supported settings are:

  • Properties
    • {@link #getDefaultDependencyView defaultDependencyView} : sap.landvisz.DependencyType (default: NETWORK_VIEW)
    • {@link #getHeight height} : int
    • {@link #getWidth width} : int
    • {@link #getTitle title} : string
    • {@link #getNetworkDependencyLabel networkDependencyLabel} : string (default: Network View)
    • {@link #getBoxDependencyLabel boxDependencyLabel} : string (default: Box View)
    • {@link #getBoxDependencyLevels boxDependencyLevels} : string[]
    • {@link #getShowDependencyNavigator showDependencyNavigator} : boolean (default: true)
    • {@link #getVisibleDependency visibleDependency} : sap.landvisz.DependencyVisibility (default: BOTH)
    • {@link #getViewType viewType} : sap.landvisz.ViewType
    • {@link #getNavigationPath navigationPath} : string
    • {@link #getHasParent hasParent} : boolean (default: true)
    • {@link #getSelectionViewPosition selectionViewPosition} : sap.landvisz.SelectionViewPosition (default: CENTER)
    • {@link #getShowClose showClose} : boolean (default: true)
    • {@link #getComponentViewLabel componentViewLabel} : string (default: Component View)
    • {@link #getDeploymentViewLabel deploymentViewLabel} : string (default: Deployment View)
    • {@link #getSolutionOptionType solutionOptionType} : sap.landvisz.OptionType
    • {@link #getSolutionType solutionType} : sap.landvisz.SolutionType
    • {@link #getShowDeploymentTypeSection showDeploymentTypeSection} : boolean (default: false)
    • {@link #getDeploymentOptionsLabel deploymentOptionsLabel} : string (default: Deployment Options :)
    • {@link #getDeploymentOptionsTooltip deploymentOptionsTooltip} : string
    • {@link #getComponentViewTooltip componentViewTooltip} : string
    • {@link #getDeploymentViewTooltip deploymentViewTooltip} : string
    • {@link #getCloseButtonTooltip closeButtonTooltip} : string
    • {@link #getPlugContentHeight plugContentHeight} : int (default: 0)
    • {@link #getConnectionLine connectionLine} : sap.landvisz.ConnectionLine (default: Line)
  • Aggregations
    • {@link #getSystems systems} : sap.landvisz.LandscapeEntity[]
    • {@link #getConnectionEntities connectionEntities} : sap.landvisz.ConnectionEntity[]
    • {@link #getConnectors connectors} : sap.landvisz.Connector[]
    • {@link #getSolutionOptions solutionOptions} : sap.landvisz.Option[]
    • {@link #getPlugContent plugContent} : sap.ui.core.Control
  • Events
    • {@link #event:close close} : fnListenerFunction or [fnListenerFunction, oListenerObject] or [oData, fnListenerFunction, oListenerObject]
    • {@link #event:loadSolutionView loadSolutionView} : fnListenerFunction or [fnListenerFunction, oListenerObject] or [oData, fnListenerFunction, oListenerObject]
In addition, all settings applicable to the base type {@link sap.landvisz.Option#constructor sap.landvisz.Option} can be used as well.
Templates.name: sap.landvisz.LandscapeViewer
Templates.helpDescription: Visualize the landscape objects in a new user experience

Templates.constructorDescription:
Constructor for a new internal/ActionBar. Accepts an object literal mSettings that defines initial property values, aggregated and associated objects as well as event handlers. See {@link sap.ui.base.ManagedObject#constructor} for a general description of the syntax of the settings object.

The supported settings are:

  • Properties
    • {@link #getActionLabel actionLabel} : string
    • {@link #getRenderingSize renderingSize} : sap.landvisz.EntityCSSSize (default: Regular)
    • {@link #getIconSrc iconSrc} : sap.ui.core.URI
    • {@link #getActionType actionType} : sap.landvisz.ActionType (default: NORMAL)
    • {@link #getMenuData menuData} : object
    • {@link #getActionTooltip actionTooltip} : string
    • {@link #getEnable enable} : boolean (default: true)
    • {@link #getChangeView changeView} : boolean (default: false)
  • Aggregations
    • {@link #getMenu menu} : sap.ui.commons.Menu[]
  • Events
    • {@link #event:select select} : fnListenerFunction or [fnListenerFunction, oListenerObject] or [oData, fnListenerFunction, oListenerObject]
In addition, all settings applicable to the base type {@link sap.ui.core.Control#constructor sap.ui.core.Control} can be used as well.
Templates.name: sap.landvisz.internal.ActionBar
Templates.helpDescription: A control that render actions of a system
